name: The Destiny of Earth
description:
Choose the destiny of Earth and your actions today will determine it in the future .
News these days are incredible about weather , Climate change is Real and it happen faster than we expect   , Heat waves , Fires , Floods people died from heat and floods and a lot of extraordinary climate we live these days , all that inspired to make this design.
1-Here on left, Earth is like mars ,It refers to Earth after destruction because of our action now .
2-On right, Earth is shinny blue refers to if we take care of it , it will remain healthy planet to live for everyone
